            "answer_color": "#5a5a5a",
            "answer_spacing": 16,
            "icon_size": 24,
            "icon_color": "#8b6f47",
            "question_1": "Is this actually chemical-free or just a claim?",
            "answer_1": "Our incense is made using natural ingredients like flower waste, herbs, and essential oils. We avoid charcoal and harmful chemicals, ensuring a cleaner and more mindful experience.",
            "question_2": "Will the fragrance actually spread across the room?",
            "answer_2": "Yes, the fragrance is designed to gently diffuse and create a calming atmosphere without being overpowering. Ideal for both small and medium-sized spaces.",
            "question_3": "Why does this cost more than local agarbatti?",
            "answer_3": "Our products use premium natural ingredients, ethical sourcing, and handcrafted processes, which ensures better quality, longer-lasting fragrance, and a healthier experience.",
            "question_4": "Is it safe for daily use around kids and elderly?",
            "answer_4": "Yes, our incense is designed to be safer than conventional options, as it is free from toxic chemicals. However, always ensure proper ventilation while using.",
            "question_5": "What if I don't like the fragrance?",
            "answer_5": "We stand by our product quality. If you're not satisfied, you can reach out to our support team for assistance or possible replacement options."
